user_query: How many High Energy Physics - Lattice articles listed in January 2020 on Arxiv had ps versions available?

1.panel_description: Identify URL for January 2020 High Energy Physics - Lattice Articles on arXiv.

1.handles: Searches for the URL on arXiv for High Energy Physics - Lattice articles for January 2020.

input_vars.name: query_jan2020_url
input_vars.description: Search query to find the URL for High Energy Physics - Lattice articles on arXiv for January 2020.
input_vars.value: arXiv High Energy Physics - Lattice articles January 2020 URL

output_vars.name: jan2020_url
output_vars.description: URL for High Energy Physics - Lattice articles on arXiv for January 2020.

2.panel_description: Access and extract January 2020 articles from the identified URL.

1.handles: Accesses the URL and extracts article details, including available formats.

input_vars.name: jan2020_url
input_vars.description: URL for accessing High Energy Physics - Lattice articles on arXiv for January 2020.

output_vars.name: article_details
output_vars.description: List of articles for January 2020 with available formats.

3.panel_description: Count the number of articles with PS versions available.

1.handles: Counts the number of articles with ps versions from the extracted list.

input_vars.name: article_details
input_vars.description: List of articles with their available formats.

output_vars.name: ps_version_count
output_vars.description: Number of articles with ps versions available.
